{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_02_02",
  "title": "ゲシっと仕事進出",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時空の狭間が閉じるまであと15時間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—15 Hours Until the Space-Time Rift Closes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.400000147,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よし、さくら達は無事『プロペラ』をゲットした\nみたいだな。このまま次の謎のヒントを見つけて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All right‚ looks like Sakura and the others safely got the “Propeller.”\nNow we just need to find the next riddle’s hint…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.500000147,
      "endTime": 10.8091382544,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.666515700001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7502.4713833999995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……って、うわぁ！　いたたた……\nなんだ……？　急に足が引っかかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Wait‚ whoa! Ouch…!\nWhat the—? My feet suddenly got tangled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0024715304,
      "endTime": 18.6578908801,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7755.4177284
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！　かかったゲシな！\n両足の靴紐をこっそり結んでおいたゲシよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geee-shi geshi geshi! Gotcha‚ geshi!\nI secretly tied your shoelaces together‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7578892588,
      "endTime": 25.504555499400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "無様な転びっぷりやなぁ、あんちゃん……\nちょっとボケっとし過ぎとちゃいますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was one pathetic fall‚ bro…\nAin’t you spacing out a bit too much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6912223378,
      "endTime": 33.8445553341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうゲシ！　ボケっとしてないで\n早く私達にBIG4の仕事を用意しろゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ geshi! Instead of zoning out‚\nhurry up and line up BIG4 jobs for us‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0578884958,
      "endTime": 40.4912221788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんて無駄に邪悪なんだ……！　というか仕事って\nまさかさくら達の仕事をかわりにやる気なのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so needlessly evil…! And jobs?\nDon’t tell me you’re planning to take over Sakura and the others’ jobs!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6912220834,
      "endTime": 48.0095669626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私達がBIG4なんだから当たり前ゲシ！　おいバルゴ\nお前に仕事を管理する任務を与えるゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! We’re the BIG4‚ geshi! Hey‚ Barugo!\nI assign you the mission of managing our jobs‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2029002387,
      "endTime": 56.8028966147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "十七歳に重大任務！　ぴちぴち十代、ひらめいた！\nまずは『ラジオ収録』で世界掌握！　チェケラ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A huge mission for a seventeen-year-old! This fresh young teen just had a brilliant idea!\nFirst‚ we conquer the world through a “radio recording”! Check it out!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.002896424,
      "endTime": 66.04956142489999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（くそっ、さくら達の大事な仕事を……！）\n（だが脱出計画がバレたら何をされるか分からない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Damn it… They’re taking Sakura and the others’ important jobs…!）\n（But if they find out about the escape plan‚ who knows what they’ll do…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2362279771,
      "endTime": 73.302146232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました、ラジオの仕事を取ってきます\nくぅっ、早く戻って来てくれ、さくら――！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Understood. I’ll arrange the radio job.\nUgh—please come back soon‚ Sakura―!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4954795081,
      "endTime": 81.51547929830001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時空の狭間が閉じるまであと12時間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—12 Hours Until the Space-Time Rift Closes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4354791839,
      "endTime": 84.7954731661,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ラジオ収録中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—During Radio Recording",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7954731661,
      "endTime": 86.0354623991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.1687957325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちゲシゲシ！　サニーピースのさくらゲシ！\n今日は星見プロのみんなでラジオ配信ゲシよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello-geshi-geshi! I’m Sakura of Sunny Peace‚ geshi!\nToday‚ all of Hoshimi Pro is bringing you this radio broadcast‚ geshi~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1354634164,
      "endTime": 95.7621350167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.968801836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなお便りサンキューメーン！\nみんなの気持ち届いてるYOYO！　Fooo！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you man―! For all the letters‚ my fans!\nYour feelings are reaching us‚ YO YO! Fooo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.968801836,
      "endTime": 103.17547383690001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6181.110127799997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.3688069223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大変だ、キャラが違い過ぎてラジオ局のスタッフが\nざわついてるぞ……！　なんとか言い訳しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad—their personalities are so different that the station staff\nare getting restless…! I need to come up with an excuse…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3688069223,
      "endTime": 110.1488069414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3354736844
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ははは……みんな新しい映画の役がなかなか\n抜けないみたいで。仕事熱心なのも困ったものですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… haha… it seems everyone’s having trouble shaking off\ntheir roles from a new movie. Such dedication can be troublesome!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3354736844,
      "endTime": 118.5804848234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3666651368
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.6471512992
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9138154227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "くそっ、このままじゃサニピの評判が大変なことに……\nだが、今のうちにさくら達に連絡が出来そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ at this rate Sunny Peace’s reputation will be in trouble…\nBut now might be my chance to contact Sakura and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7471518079,
      "endTime": 128.4352242986,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_telepathy-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14725.554434499998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ビビビビビーッ！　こちら{user}！\nさくら！　みんな！　そっちは大丈夫か！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bibibibibi―! This is {user}!\nSakura! Everyone! Are you okay over there!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6285575747,
      "endTime": 134.1327072979,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_telepathy-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 135.2393739264
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　それが、なんだか\n様子がおかしいんです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Well‚ the thing is…\nsomething feels really strange…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3060411017,
      "endTime": 142.30874362400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 142.5020768047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ここ、どんどんぐにゃぐにゃしてきた気が\nするんですわ！　一体何が起こっているんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like this place is getting more and more warped\nand squishy! What on earth is happening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5020768047,
      "endTime": 149.8030929448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 149.989759497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　さくら達には伝えていなかったな……\n実は、時空の狭間は……あと12時間で閉じる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right! I hadn’t told you yet…\nActually‚ the space-time rift will close in 12 hours…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.989759497,
      "endTime": 158.8876811624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 159.8077832104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "時空が閉じる……って出られなくなるってこと！？\nなんで言ってなかったのよバカ！　早く脱出しないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rift closing… means we won’t be able to get out!?\nWhy didn’t you tell us‚ idiot!? We need to escape fast!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.8077832104,
      "endTime": 167.2204169157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 167.4337499819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
